snippet.title: Breakout: Recharged - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the launch trailer for Breakout: Recharged, a reimagining of the classic arcade game.

The game features an endless mode, local co-op, and tasks players to compete in a series of 50 increasingly challenging levels.

Breakout: Recharged is available now on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, Atari VCS, and PC (via Steam and Epic Games Store).

#GameTrailers #Gaming #Breakout
